      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This driver-grade example boasts a linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline, facilitated by eight individual throttle bodies. Crucial preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, has been completed. The chassis retains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a limited-slip M-Variable differential. While showing light cosmetic wear consistent with its mileage, the hydraulic steering rack and suspension bushings remain tight, providing an unadulterated analog driving experience.",
