    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained example that perfectly balances performance and daily usability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front valence consistent with careful road use. All body panels are straight with factory-consistent gaps. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership; the premium leather seats show only light bolstering wear, and the dashboard remains free of any cracks or sun damage. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection just completed. The engine pulls smoothly through the rev range, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter, offering a premium driving experience without the 'mint' price tag. Includes two sets of keys and a complete service history log.",
